  "body": "### Description\r\n[Design](https://www.figma.com/file/qHfFm7C9LwtXpfdbxssCK3/Kuba%E2%8E%9CDesktop---Communities?type=design&node-id=37206%3A87272&mode=design&t=WK5aiGMX4bnXgd41-1)\r\n\r\nHere it is a summary of all **notifications** and **toasts** needed for the `Community Ownership Transfer`:\r\n\r\n---       \r\n**Sender NOTIFICATION CENTER:**\r\n1. Your device is no longer the control node for \"Community Name\"\r\n\r\n**Sender TOASTS:**\r\n1. Sending Owner-CommunityName token\r\n2. Owner-CommunityName token sent\r\n3. Your device is no longer the control node for \"Community Name\". Your ownership and admin rights for \"Community Name\" have been transferred to the new owner.\r\n\r\n---\r\n**Receiver NOTIFICATION CENTER :**\r\n1. You received the Owner token for \"Community Name\" --> Button to `Finalise ownership` flow needed\r\n2. Your device is now the control node for \"Community Name\" --> Button to community admin page\r\n3. \"Community name\" smart contract updated failed --> something wrong after accepting ownership\r\n4. You received the Owner token for \"Community Name\" / Ownership Declined --> When receiver declines to be the owner \r\n\r\n**Receiver TOASTS:**\r\n\r\n1. You received the Owner token for \"Community Name\". To finalize ownership, make your device the control node. --> Link to `Finalise ownership` flow needed\r\n2. Updating \"Community Name\" smart contract --> After accepting ownership\r\n3. Your device is now the control node for \"Community Name\". You now have full community admin rigths. --> Link to community admin page\r\n5. \"Community name\" smart contract amended --> After accepting ownership.\r\n6. \"Community name\" smart contract update failed --> something wrong after accepting ownership\r\n7. You declined ownership of \"Community Name\" --> When receiver declines to be the owner ",
