    "body": "On this [PR](m/status-im/status-desktop/pull/12288), the following integration points have been added:\r\n- `ui/app/AppLayouts/Chat/ChatLayout.qml` --> `isPendingOwnershipRequest` property. It should be used to capture that the `token owner` is received into one of the wallet accounts of the future community owner and this user is able to finalise the change ownership process / request. \r\n- `ui/app/AppLayouts/Chat/ChatLayout.qml` --> `ownershipDeclined` signal will be raised when the future owner declines the request. At that point the proper notification / toast need to be updated with the new info.\r\n- `ui/imports/shared/stores/CommunityTokensStore.qml` --> `updateSmartContract` function should be used to start the needed smart contract update process.\r\n\r\nThere's a missing `finalise transfer ownership`  entry point in UI from **notification center** that needs to be coverd also in here:\r\n![Screenshot 2023-09-15 at 13 08 35](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/97019400/596cbddf-1925-478d-8c02-a52f23cda170)\r\n**NOTE:** It should be nice if the `finaliseOwnershipPopup` added in `ui/app/AppLayouts/Chat/ChatLayout.qml` is used also for this missing flow so we will end up with just a central point with the component definition. See the previous PR mentioned in here as a reference.\r\n",
